name: Mount of Khafr
description:
Mountains are protectors of our village, and all the villages next to us. This part of desert is a bit colder because of the mountains that surrounds it, therefore you can see a lot of gardens and greens  unlike the other cities in desert. This mountain, a spiky one shaped like an ocean wave represents the village "Khafr". It's another village next to ours. 
--
35mm black and white photography
